headline: IDEX Earnings Preview: What to Expect
summary: Industrial giant IDEX is gearing up to release its third-quarter results by the end of October, and analysts expect low-single-digit growth in earnings.

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock on Our Watchlist and 2 We Turn Down
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.
